Class DocumentAttributes

  • java.lang.Object
    • craterdog.smart.SmartObject<DocumentAttributes>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    craterdog.core.Composite, Comparable<DocumentAttributes>

    public class DocumentAttributes
extends craterdog.smart.SmartObject<DocumentAttributes>
    This class defines the attributes that make up a document that can be notarized.
    Author:
    Derk Norton
